<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="report-v">report <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'pɔːt/    美 /rɪ'pɔːrt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>报告；报道；汇报：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They will report the matter in the newspaper. 
他们将在报纸上报道这件事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The school newspaper sent her to <strong>report on</strong> the contest. 
校报派她去报道本次竞赛。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>report + doing sth / (that) 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The girl reported seeing UFOs. / The girl reported that she had seen UFOs.
该少女报告说，她看到了不明飞行物。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>be reported to do sth / it is reported that ...：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The accident is reported to have occurred on the first Sunday in February. / It is reported that the accident occurred on the first Sunday in February. 
据报道事故发生在二月的第一个星期日。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>举报；告发：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like to report a robbery. 
我要举报一起抢劫案。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should <strong>report him to</strong> the police. 
我们应向警察举报他。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>报到：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All visitors must <strong>report to</strong> the reception desk on arrival. 
所有来访者到达后务必在接待处报到。</p></div></div>